Quote: I know that a number of the cows under test this season will be given a better opportunity next season, since more members will provide maize or other feeds as soiling-crops in addition to the ordinary pasture. The value of soiling-crops is evidenced by the yields of two herds pasturing on opposite sides of the same road.
